    "The authors test its performance in multiple Cloud-Edge settings and improve latency with a reduction in mean response time.",
    "To address real-time performance and security issues of tasks, Singh et al. [45] design a scheduling algorithm 'RT-SANE'.",
    "Through extensive experiments, they show that the algorithm attains a higher ''success ratio'' in comparison with existing approaches.To manage the dynamic allocation of resources and services in the Cloud-to-Edge Continuum, Tusa et al. [46] provide a unified resource management approach comprising both cloud data center and network resources.",
    "Their goal is to reduce the 'silo-effect' (isolation of functionalities, resources and services) and provide 'end-to-end slices' (comprising compute, storage and network slices) to perform orchestration of heterogeneous resources and user specific on-demand services ensuring security, isolation and optimized performance.",
